WHEREAS, she is survived by her brother, Boone Vastine and his wife, Carolyn;
her daughter, Cheryl Jones and her husband, Rowley, and their children, Shelby Neuman and
her husband, Nick, and Grayson Jones; her son, Richard Wood and his wife, Dr. Rebecca
Adcock; her stepdaughter, Nancy Readinger and her children, Alexa Alexander and Andrew
Readinger; her stepson, Jeff Hughes and his wife, Tammy, and his children, Jessica Stewart
and her husband, Chad, and Campbell Hughes and his wife, Amy Paige; as well as five
great-granddaughters, a future great-grandson, and numerous nieces and nephews; and
WHEREAS, Barbara leaves behind a legacy of service and will be remembered for
her warmth, wit, and sincere interest in others, qualities that enriched the lives of all who
knew her.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby express its sincere condolences upon the passing of Barbara Vastine Hughes.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
family of Barbara Vastine Hughes.
